{"tid":1075929,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大退休法律教授：中國司法制度完全違反人權　港府修例放棄自治","createTime":"2019-03-24T13:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T16:33:37.000Z","uid":47714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68cbbea4b03512345f3399c547a6303767834fe1","tid":1075929,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/272280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F272280%2F&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8l9PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=3915f358\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/272280/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmSGnHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbmSGnHs.png&h=3062ca5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴大為（Michael Davis）指出，大陸和香港的司法制度不同，香港以辯方為主導，盡力保障被告人權，控辯雙方可以就證供辯論。但大陸則是以控方為主導，聆訊有時候不會公開，辯方甚至沒機會傳召證人作交叉盤問，形容大陸司法制度「完全違反人權」。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，不同司法管轄區簽訂引渡協議，要考慮對方聆訊過程是否公平，以及是否符合國際對人權的期望，亦要視乎對方有沒有法治和司法獨立的法院。而大陸的司法制度和法官不時受到政府干預，是國際認知的事實。"},{"pid":"685711d2b69aff8eba8606623297288387799136","tid":1075929,"uid":229183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"香港？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96bb5cdfeb7d7d70224b6ca38ca03726cb4a1ce","tid":1075929,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"中國香港。<br />\n唔係 英殖香港了。<br />\n<br />\n算尻數la"}]}